h2. RSpec on Rails - Specifying Models

Model Specs live in $RAILS_ROOT/spec/models/ and provide access to fixtures.

h2. Expectations

Model Specs support the following custom expectations:

h3. Records

<ruby>
Model.should_have(:no).records
Model.should_have(1).record
Model.should_have(3).records
</ruby>

This is an alias for <code>Model.find(:all).length.should_eql 3</code>.

